0dbb6","tid":1811295,"uid":59137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"我對港獨既理解係唔可以講但可以做, 同台獨一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得港獨同台獨唔同<br />\n台灣人可以一人一票選總統 所以佢地可以只做唔講<br />\n我地連立法會都冇普選 想靜靜雞做 就只能武裝革命<br />\n但係喺香港要成功以武力革命 個難度係極高<br />\n所以我係支持經濟攬炒 逼中共喺經濟同主權之間做抉擇<br />\n逼到中共投降 放棄香港<br />\n<br />\n當然 我都唔知邊個啱 只係想討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fccb90709ca45ba60c56d3c3c24384d5adc2620","tid":1811295,"uid":89584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"045c67fede1b4aef11afc616264be933ea9624dc","tid":1811295,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"好呀 搞港獨集會啦<br />\n我係屋企睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"我之所以話要討論同宣傳<br />\n係因為連登可以隱藏我地身份<br />\n所以我地可以暢所欲言<br />\n如果有一日 港獨成為主流意見<br />\n自然搞得成港獨集會<br />\n<br />\n依家只係踏出緊第一步: 就係話俾同路人知 支持獨立嘅 唔止你一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48c899efb7ef1903498da8550cfe51c4825368e","tid":1811295,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32902c449f13b803d2d0747dce2465d70f20f909","tid":1811295,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da48a1957d11abe65662941dc1399a12722985f","tid":1811295,"uid":336872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"思路幾清晰，空推一下～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},